Create a csv of the first 5 presidents of the United states with their names, age when they started office, year they started office, and number of years they served
Sure! Here is your CSV file. Please note that this includes only five current U.S. Presidents as per the latest available information on the Wikipedia page for presidents since 1945. If you need data for a different period or for historical figures, please adjust accordingly.

```csv
"President","Age at Start of Office","Year Started Office","Number of Years Served"
George Washington,63,"July 2 Presidential Election",18
James Madison,59,"January 30th Constitutional Amendment",7.5
Abraham Lincoln,48,"July 2 Presidential Election",10
Benjamin Franklin I,47,"July 2 Presidential Election",6
Thomas Jefferson II,46,"January 30th Constitutional Amendment",9.5
```
